Best Practices to follow:
1- Never HardCode.
2- Keep right things at the right place.
3- Make the Framwork little robust
Naming conventions to follow:
1- CLass or Interface name: ShwetaKatheriya (Initials caps)
2- Final Constant values: SHWETAKATHERIYA or SHWETA_KATHERIYA (All caps)
3- Method name: shwetaKatheriya (CamelCasing)
4- Package Name: shwetakatheriya (All small)